Haryana
Nov 21, 2014
Abduction
Description:
			The Haryana police have registered cases against three youths in separate incidents for allegedly luring minor girls and eloping with them.

In the first incident, Rahul, a resident of Agwanpur, complained that her 17-year-old sister was lured by Rahul who ran away with her on the pretext of marriage, 

In a similar incident, Shripal, a resident of Chaysa, alleged that his neighbour Pawan lured his sister into eloping with him.

In another incident, Ramjeet, a resident of Rajeev Nagar, alleged that an unidentified man lured his 14-year-old daughter to elope with him.

